<div id="review_2369143428" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2369143428" />
    <a title="Mickenzie Jensen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/25033374-mickenzie-jensen"><img alt="Mickenzie Jensen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1382639877p2/25033374.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2369143428?book_show_action=true">Apr 22, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mickenzie Jensen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mickenzie Jensen" href="/user/show/25033374-mickenzie-jensen">Mickenzie Jensen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/32467262-hank-brodt-holocaust-memoirs">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2369143428" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1351814129768192728"><strong>An amazing story of survival</strong><br/><br/>I have always been interested in hearing the stories of holocaust survivors. Even as a child, I was moved by their stories of cruelty, horror, and survival. I am not Jewish, and none of my friends or family are Jewish, yet I have always been deeply affected by the way people have mistreated the Jewish people throughout the world. As I continue to struggle to understand the cruelty of the hateful, I am constantly amazed at the powerful hope of the survivors of their vi</span>
  <span id="freeText1351814129768192728" style="display:none"><strong>An amazing story of survival</strong><br /><br />I have always been interested in hearing the stories of holocaust survivors. Even as a child, I was moved by their stories of cruelty, horror, and survival. I am not Jewish, and none of my friends or family are Jewish, yet I have always been deeply affected by the way people have mistreated the Jewish people throughout the world. As I continue to struggle to understand the cruelty of the hateful, I am constantly amazed at the powerful hope of the survivors of their vile deeds. <br />This was truly one of the best holocaust memoirs I have read. The fact that this amazing man not only lived through the horrors of the holocaust, but did so with his faith and humanity intact, is beyond inspiring. If he can keep his faith after enduring so much, perhaps I can too.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1351814129768192728" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
