              <span id="reviewTextContainer3935073471" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18158348467767438946">A deeply moving account of one man’s determination to survive the unimaginable. I have given this book five stars, not because of any literary merit, but to draw attention to a book all should read. May Henk’s memory be a blessing.</span>

          </span>
