<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/34235504-the-dead-years"><img alt="The Dead Years: Holocaust Memoirs (Holocaust Survivor Memoirs World War II Book 3)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1486930526l/34235504._SY75_.jpg" />
